  16. # The Makefile for ocamltest

  18. ROOTDIR = ..

  20. include $(ROOTDIR)/Makefile.common
  21. include $(ROOTDIR)/Makefile.best_binaries

  23. # List of source files from which ocamltest is compiled
  24. # (all the different sorts of files are derived from this)

  26. # ocamltest has two components: its core and the OCaml "plugin"
  27. # which is actually built into the tool but clearly separated from its core

  29. core := \
  30.   run_$(UNIX_OR_WIN32).c run_stubs.c \
  31.   ocamltest_config.mli ocamltest_config.ml.in \
  32.   ocamltest_unix.mli ocamltest_unix.ml \
  33.   ocamltest_stdlib.mli ocamltest_stdlib.ml \
  34.   run_command.mli run_command.ml \
  35.   filecompare.mli filecompare.ml \
  36.   variables.mli variables.ml \
  37.   environments.mli environments.ml \
  38.   result.mli result.ml \
  39.   actions.mli actions.ml \
  40.   tests.mli tests.ml \
  41.   strace.mli strace.ml \
  42.   tsl_ast.mli tsl_ast.ml \
  43.   tsl_parser.mly \
  44.   tsl_lexer.mli tsl_lexer.mll \
  45.   modifier_parser.mli modifier_parser.ml \
  46.   tsl_semantics.mli tsl_semantics.ml \
  47.   builtin_variables.mli builtin_variables.ml \
  48.   actions_helpers.mli actions_helpers.ml \
  49.   builtin_actions.mli builtin_actions.ml

  51. ocaml_plugin := \
  52.   ocaml_backends.mli ocaml_backends.ml \
  53.   ocaml_filetypes.mli ocaml_filetypes.ml \
  54.   ocaml_variables.mli ocaml_variables.ml \
  55.   ocaml_modifiers.mli ocaml_modifiers.ml \
  56.   ocaml_directories.mli ocaml_directories.ml \
  57.   ocaml_files.mli ocaml_files.ml \
  58.   ocaml_flags.mli ocaml_flags.ml \
  59.   ocaml_commands.mli ocaml_commands.ml \
  60.   ocaml_tools.mli ocaml_tools.ml \
  61.   ocaml_compilers.mli ocaml_compilers.ml \
  62.   ocaml_toplevels.mli ocaml_toplevels.ml \
  63.   ocaml_actions.mli ocaml_actions.ml \
  64.   ocaml_tests.mli ocaml_tests.ml

  66. sources := $(core) $(ocaml_plugin) \
  67.   options.mli options.ml \
  68.   main.mli main.ml

  70. # List of .ml files used for ocamldep and to get the list of modules

  72. ml_files := \
  73.   $(filter %.ml, \
  74.     $(subst .ml.in,.ml,$(subst .mll,.ml,$(subst .mly,.ml,$(sources)))) \
  75.   )

  77. cmo_files := $(ml_files:.ml=.cmo)

  79. cmx_files := $(ml_files:.ml=.cmx)

  81. # List of .mli files for ocamldep
  82. mli_files := \
  83.   $(filter %.mli,$(subst .mly,.mli,$(sources)))

  85. cmi_files := $(mli_files:.mli=.cmi)

  87. c_files := $(filter %.c, $(sources))

  89. o_files := $(c_files:.c=.$(O))

  91. lexers := $(filter %.mll,$(sources))

  93. parsers := $(filter %.mly,$(sources))

  95. dependencies_generated_prereqs := \
  96.   ocamltest_unix.ml \
  97.   $(lexers:.mll=.ml) \
  98.   $(parsers:.mly=.mli) $(parsers:.mly=.ml)

  100. generated := $(dependencies_generated_prereqs) $(parsers:.mly=.output)

  102. bytecode_modules := $(o_files) $(cmo_files)

  104. native_modules := $(o_files) $(cmx_files)

  106. directories := $(addprefix $(ROOTDIR)/,utils bytecomp parsing \
  107.                                        compilerlibs file_formats)

  109. include_directories := $(addprefix -I , $(directories))

  111. flags := $(STDLIBFLAGS) -g $(include_directories) \
  112.   -strict-sequence -strict-formats \
  113.   -w +a-4-9-41-42-44-45-48 -warn-error +A

  115. ocamlc = $(BEST_OCAMLC) $(flags)

  117. ocamlopt = $(BEST_OCAMLOPT) $(flags)

  119. .SECONDARY: $(lexers:.mll=.ml) $(parsers:.mly=.mli) $(parsers:.mly=.ml)

  121. .PHONY: all allopt opt.opt # allopt and opt.opt are synonyms
  122. all: ocamltest$(EXE)
  123. allopt: ocamltest.opt$(EXE)
  124. opt.opt: allopt

  126. compdeps_names=ocamlcommon ocamlbytecomp
  127. compdeps_paths=$(addprefix $(ROOTDIR)/compilerlibs/,$(compdeps_names))
  128. deps_paths = \
  129.   $(compdeps_paths) $(addprefix $(ocamltest_unix_path)/,$(ocamltest_unix_name))
  130. deps_byte=$(addsuffix .cma,$(deps_paths))
  131. deps_opt=$(addsuffix .cmxa,$(deps_paths))

  133. $(eval $(call PROGRAM_SYNONYM,ocamltest))

  135. ocamltest_unix.%: flags+=$(ocamltest_unix_include) -opaque

  137. ocamltest$(EXE): $(deps_byte) $(bytecode_modules)
  138.         $(V_LINKC)$(ocamlc_cmd) $(ocamltest_unix_include)-custom -o $@ $^

  140. %.cmo: %.ml $(deps_byte)
  141.         $(V_OCAMLC)$(ocamlc) -c $<

  143. $(eval $(call PROGRAM_SYNONYM,ocamltest.opt))

  145. ocamltest.opt$(EXE): $(deps_opt) $(native_modules)
  146.         $(V_LINKOPT)$(ocamlopt_cmd) $(ocamltest_unix_include)-o $@ $^

  148. %.cmx: %.ml $(deps_opt)
  149.         $(V_OCAMLOPT)$(ocamlopt) -c $<

  151. %.cmi: %.mli $(deps_byte)
  152.         $(V_OCAMLC)$(ocamlc) -c $<

  154. ocamltest_unix.ml: ocamltest_unix_$(ocamltest_unix_impl).ml
  155.         $(V_GEN)echo '# 1 "$<"' > $@ && \
  156.         cat $< >> $@

  158. # Manual

  160. .PHONY: doc

  162. doc: ocamltest.html

  164. ocamltest.html: ocamltest.org
  165.         pandoc -s --toc -N -f org -t html -o $@ $<

  167. .PHONY: clean
  168. clean:
  169.         rm -rf ocamltest ocamltest.exe ocamltest.opt ocamltest.opt.exe
  170.         rm -rf *.o *.obj *.cm*
  171.         rm -rf $(generated)
  172.         rm -f ocamltest.html
  173.         rm -rf $(DEPDIR)

  175. ifeq "$(COMPUTE_DEPS)" "true"
  176. include $(addprefix $(DEPDIR)/, $(c_files:.c=.$(D)))
  177. endif

  179. .PHONY: distclean
  180. distclean: clean
  181.         rm -f ocamltest_config.ml

  183. $(DEPDIR)/%.$(D): %.c | $(DEPDIR)
  184.         $(V_CCDEPS)$(DEP_CC) $(OC_CPPFLAGS) $(CPPFLAGS) $< -MT '$*.$(O)' -MF $@

  186. .PHONY: depend
  187. depend: $(dependencies_generated_prereqs)
  188.         $(V_OCAMLDEP)$(OCAMLDEP_CMD) $(mli_files) $(ml_files) > .depend

  190. -include .depend
